data.description: SELLER OFFERING 2% INCENTIVE WITH ACCEPTABLE OFFER! USE TOWARDS RATE BUYDOWN OR CLOSING COSTS AND PRE-PAIDS. Step into this charming residence and be greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere. This spacious 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and style. With it's open-concept design, guest room that boasts an ensuite bathroom, and modern kitchen, this easy-to-care-for home has everything you've been searching for. Once inside, you'll be greeted by an open and inviting floor plan that is perfect for both family living and entertaining. The well-appointed kitchen features modern appliances, ample counter space, and plenty of storage, making it a chef's delight. It effortlessly flows into the generous living and dining areas, ensuring that you can host gatherings with ease. The master bedroom is a tranquil retreat, complete with an ensuite bathroom that offers a spa-like atmosphere, perfect for unwinding after a long day. Three additional bedrooms provide plenty of space for family members or guests. The guest room with its ensuite bathroom is a particularly enticing feature, ensuring your visitors have their own private oasis. One of the standout features of this property is the screened lanai, a perfect spot to enjoy the beautiful St. Augustine weather year-round. Whether you're sipping your morning coffee or hosting a BBQ with friends, this outdoor space will quickly become your favorite spot. The easy to care for yard is a bonus for those seeking a beautiful property without the hassle of constant upkeep. Spend more time enjoying your home and less time tending to the lawn. Located in St. Augustine, you'll have easy access to all the city has to offer, including historic sites, shopping, dining, and beautiful beaches. This home is the epitome of Florida living with its ideal combination of comfort and convenience.
